Misc scripts
============

A collection of shell scripts for various purposes.

- backup: Make backups using find and tar
- ccma-dl: Download media files from the CCMA
- cpu-usage: Show CPU usage
- free-space: Show available space
- mem-usage: Show memory usage
- play-stream: Play media streams with mplayer
- unixfy: Rename files using Unix-friendly filenames

Installation
------------

    $ aclocal
    $ automake -c --add-missing
    $ autoconf
    $ ./configure
    $ make install
